data.text:

1982: Martin Furlong, Mick Lowry, Liam Connor, Mick Fitzgerald, Pat Fitzgerald, Sean Lowry, Liam Currams, Tomas Connor, Padraig Dunne, John Guinan, Richie Connor, Gerry Carroll, Johnny Mooney, Matt Connor, Brendan Lowry. Subs: Stephen. Darby, Seamus Darby
